---
title: Chimichurri Chicken Drumsticks & Roast Veggies with Mayonnaise & Roasted Almonds
description: Tried and true chicken and veg just had a major makeover! This chicken is marinated in chimichurri seasoning and honey for a
sweet and savoury hit, and is accompanied by a rainbow of roasted veggies. A dollop of creamy mayo is the perfect addition to
tie it all together.
